ActSahtu Dene and Metis Land Claim Settlement Act
PrecisOrder approving an amendment to be made to the SAHTU DENE AND METIS COMPREHENSIVE LAND CLAIM AGREEMENT which allows the Surveyer General to place a series of monuments approximating the mean position of a natural feature and thereby enable him to complete the surveys within the Sahtu Settlement Area.
